{"tid":703282,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好似我咁每個月keep住病要睇幾次醫生？","createTime":"2018-06-15T15:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T11:49:28.000Z","uid":42499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c51ee67f66aa3cd24a09e8874ad046846dd86bfa","tid":703282,"uid":42499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:12:23.000Z","msg":"我諗我工作關係啦<br />\n經常上呼吸道感染 喉嚨發炎嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近呢年開始病得比較多<br />\n體重跌咗6-7kg<br />\n以往睇完西醫食藥一個星期左右都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近呢3個月病親都坐底2星期先斷尾<br />\n有冇過來人分享下可以點樣調理好身體？<br />\n利申 食飯嗰啲正常份量 有食三餐 幾乎每日一水果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875dc47fa48b44a0701ae92b54db91cebfe85b42","tid":703282,"uid":160591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:15:52.000Z","msg":"係咩工作?<br />\n你要由源頭去解決喎<br />\n成日食藥會令你本身越來越弱"},{"pid":"4fa83da842e53ae0a29aea13c6d62c946de058ab","tid":703282,"uid":30708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:34:19.000Z","msg":"每個月拎幾日病假就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a61b5993f7c1c140aed2e5acd7912ee46aabf8c","tid":703282,"uid":13248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:57:13.000Z","msg":"平時有無做下運動"},{"pid":"5a379701ea9af23dec145fc1a9ad9b6a3a4358a5","tid":703282,"uid":31796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:47:26.000Z","msg":"本身有長期病<br />\n每個月都要請一兩日病假<br />\n最近俾HR出信話我請得太多病假<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef10d524ee6cdc1774821e8c1f7e338c2264870","tid":703282,"uid":161918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T17:08:25.000Z","msg":"轉行啦<br />\n<br />\n返工返到長期病患<br />\n<br />\n就算你大命<br />\n<br />\n老左有排你受"},{"pid":"2283fef3468843b49d2ce79dcc5f6850a3f2a320","tid"